  "2 cos²x - 1 = 0 gives cos²x = 1/2, so cos x = ±√2/2. This yields x = π/4, 3π/4, 5π/4, and 7π/4.": "",
  "Solve: sin²x - sin x = 0 on [0, 2π).": "",
